[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Pagebanner default.jpg"]]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["File:10361 Stadhuis van Lier.jpg"],["thumb"],["City hall in Lier"]]},"\n",{"type":"'''","value":[{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.lier.be Lier"]}]}," is a city of about 30,000 inhabitants in the province of ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Antwerp (province)"],["Antwerp"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Belgium"]]},". \n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Understand"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n\nLier can be conveniently reached by car. Highways aren't that close. It's halfway between E19 ( ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Antwerp"]]}," to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Brussels"]]}," ) and E313 ( ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Antwerp"]]}," to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Liege"]]},". The national roads connect the town with the highways and other close-by cities, like the N10 to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Antwerp"]]},", N14 to ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Mechelen"]]}," and N13 to the E313. Like many towns in Belgium it is a problem, however, to get rid of your car in the city center.\n\nLier is connected by rail to quite a few major Belgian cities, including ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Antwerp"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Mechelen"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Herentals"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Aarschot"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Leuven"]]}," and ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Brussels"]]},". The connection to Antwerp is especially good, from which any other destination within Belgium can easily be reached. To plan your trip, you can consult the website of NMBS ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.b-rail.be\/main\/E\/"]}," for national and international travels. The train station is located fairly close to the city center, only some 10 minutes in walking distance.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["Public transportation"]},"\nThe public transport company ",{"type":"'''","value":[{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.delijn.be De Lijn"]}]}," has a number of bus lines through Lier. \n\n",{"type":"===","value":["On foot"]},"\nBest method to discover Lier. Most places of interest are in the center of the city and lay only a couple of minutes from each other.\n\n",{"type":"===","value":["Bicycle"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["see"],["name=Zimmertoren"],["alt="],["url="],["email="],["address="],["lat=51.12911"],["long=4.57008"],["directions=Zimmerplein"],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price=Entrance â‚¬3"],["content=Small tower with astronomical display."]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["Beguinage"]},", UNESCO World Heritage Site"]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["The St. Gummarus Church"]},", Gothic architecture, 14th century."]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"'''","value":["The Town hall"]},", Rococo architecture, 18th century.With ",{"type":"'''","value":["belfry tower"]}," from 1369."]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name=Boat tour"],["alt="],["url="],["email="],["address="],["lat=51.12876"],["long=4.56995"],["directions=Next to Zimmerplein"],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content=On river Nete. (Not in winter)"]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Learn"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Buy"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Eat"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" Quite a few restaurants around Zimmerplein, Grote Markt and the street in between (Eikelstraat). Mostly French and Italian cuisine."]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["eat"],["name=Baja Sardinia"],["alt="],["url="],["email="],["address="],["lat=51.13041"],["long=4.56928"],["directions=Eikelstraat"],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content=Fairly good Italian food. Normal prices. Fast service."]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["eat"],["name=Toscana"],["alt="],["url="],["email="],["address="],["lat=51.12961"],["long=4.56952"],["directions=Zimmerplein"],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content=Basic Italian cuisine. Affordable prices. Not very busy. Great gelato (ice cream)."]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Drink"]},"\n\nMost of the nightlife is centered around Zimmerplein in local pubs.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Sleep"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["sleep"],["name=Best Western Zimmerhotel"],["alt="],["url="],["email="],["address="],["lat=51.12440"],["long=4.57527"],["directions="],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["checkin=4PM"],["checkout=11AM"],["price="],["content=Medium size hotel, for business customers and tourists. Nice and big rooms. Breakfast only. No bar. Prices include use of the fitness center next door."]]}]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Go next"]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["WikiPedia:Lier, Belgium"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["geo"],["51.1333"],["4.5667"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["IsPartOf"],["Antwerp (province)"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["outlinecity"]]},{"type":"[[","value":[["nl:Lier"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Commons:Lier, Belgium"]]}]